title: Zartharim

properties.name: description
properties.value: Zartharim was a settlement from the Fourth Age and hometown of the hero Aivas. Nothing else is known about it, and it presumably no longer exists or goes by a different name.

rawContent:
'''Zartharim''' was a settlement from the [[Fourth Age]] and hometown of the hero [[Aivas]]. Nothing else is known about it, and it presumably no longer exists or goes by a different name.
